---
/* About page — comparison mocks (revised scope).
   ------------------------------------------------------------------
   2026-05-24. Two sections only on the About page now: Origins +
   Story. The flower legend and the 24-carat-gold-leaf signature are
   OUT of scope — they already live on the home page. The Manifesto
   direction (prior Option B) is OUT.

   Origins structure is locked to Pax's four-beat chronology
   (Argopuro / the seed / Jember / Time). What varies across this
   surface is the IMAGE TREATMENT per beat. Five variants (Pax's
   Part 3, Options 1–5). Pax recommends Option 4 (asymmetric
   editorial, varied per beat).

   Story direction is undecided. A single placeholder treatment
   sits at the foot of the page so Stephane sees how the page
   closes. Quiet, type-led, founder content from the brand pager.

   Direct-URL only. NOT linked from the nav. The live `/about` page
   stays UNTOUCHED. Same pattern as `/story-mocks`,
   `/product-mocks`, `/volage-header-mocks`.

   Sources of truth.
     · Image-treatment variants: `about-origins-image-research.md`,
       Part 3 (Options 1–5).
     · Origins prose: `mariposa - brand (2026-05-20).html` Origins
       section, split across Pax's four beats.
     · Story prose: same brand pager, signature + founder sections. */

import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import cigarVolage  from '../assets/cigar-volage.png';
import cigarCaprice from '../assets/cigar-caprice.png';

/* Option 2 placeholder atmosphere — existing hero stock standing in
   for commissioned shots, so Stephane can read the full-bleed
   cinematic composition. Final shots commissioned per brief. */
import o2Land from '../assets/hero-mp-1.jpg';
import o2Seed from '../assets/hero-mp-3.jpg';
import o2Hand from '../assets/hero-mp-5.jpg';
import o2Time from '../assets/hero-mp-6.jpg';

const o2PlaceholderNote = 'Placeholder atmosphere — final shot to be commissioned per the brief';

/* ─── Origins beat content — verbatim from brand pager,
       partitioned across Pax's four beats ──────────────────────── */

/* Beat 1 — Argopuro (the land). The 1859 anchor + the volcanic-
   earth marriage paragraph (first sentence only — the rest of the
   land/seed material goes to beat 2 so the seed beat has its own
   story to carry). */
const beatLandEyebrow = 'Argopuro · East Java';
const beatLandBody =
  'Mariposa is hand-rolled in Jember, East Java. A region whose rich cigar-making heritage dates back to 1859. The wrapper, binder, and filler are all born from Havana-seed tobacco that has spent nearly two decades acclimatising to Jember’s volcanic earth.';

/* Beat 2 — The seed (Pak Abdul Kahar Muzakir + the 20-year
   acclimatisation). Promoted to its own beat per Pax. */
const beatSeedEyebrow = 'The seed · Twenty years';
const beatSeedBody =
  'Jember is also home to Pak Abdul Kahar Muzakir, a cigar aficionado and industry veteran who has dedicated his life to a singular pursuit: capturing the essence of Cuban tradition by cultivating Havana seeds in Indonesian soil. The result is a perfect marriage of flavour profiles, blending the signature spice and oiliness of Cuban genetics with Java’s signature earthy sweetness.';

/* Beat 3 — Jember (the workshop, the female rollers, the entubado
   and triple cap). The credibility payload. */
const beatHandEyebrow = 'Jember · The workshop';
const beatHandBody =
  'Mariposa cigars are entirely hand-rolled by a dedicated team of female rollers, mirroring Cuba’s revered torcedoras, many of whom come from families that have worked tobacco for generations. Using long-filler, three-part construction, and entubado bunching for a flawlessly even draw, each cigar is finished with a classic Cuban triple cap. Every single stick is draw-tested and inspected by hand before it leaves the workshop, guaranteeing a flawless smoking experience.';

/* Beat 4 — Time (24-month fermentation, 12-month ageing). */
const beatTimeEyebrow = 'Time · Three years';
const beatTimeBody =
  'Patience is central to the craft. Honouring the tradition of Cuba’s escogida, each leaf type is sorted and fermented separately for 24 months, then rested for another twelve. That is close to three years from leaf to finished cigar, a slow maturation that yields rich flavours and an undeniably smooth smoke.';

/* ─── Story placeholder content (brand pager, Story section) ─── */
const storyFounderParas = [
  'Mariposa’s story begins with a journey. Driven by a lifelong taste for cigars, founder Stephane Zermatten followed his curiosity to the tobacco fields of East Java.',
  'What he discovered inspired him to craft a blend for his own humidor and closest friends. Yet, as word spread and a wider circle grew curious, he knew it couldn’t remain a private reserve. The brand was born to bring this unique cigar to a growing community in Bali and beyond.',
  'Today, Mariposa captures the rich, multi-cultural soul of cigars, giving friends around the world the perfect excuse to light up, slow down, and share a good conversation. Whatever the hour.',
];
const storyKicker =
  'A Havana-seed smoke, gold-leaf adorned, for the people who don’t wait for special occasions, but create them.';

/* ─── Placeholder caption helpers ─────────────────────────────── */
const capLand     = 'PLACEHOLDER: Argopuro range — tobacco field at the foot of the volcano, landscape, golden-hour or overcast.';
const capSeed     = 'PLACEHOLDER: Pak Abdul Kahar Muzakir — portrait, hands on a Havana seedling at the Jember nursery.';
const capHand     = 'PLACEHOLDER: Jember rolling room — torcedoras at work, hands and leaf. The shot of the section.';
const capTime     = 'PLACEHOLDER: ageing room — rows of bundled cigars in maturation.';
const capTimeA    = 'PLACEHOLDER: escogida fermentation — leaf bundles, month 4.';
const capTimeB    = 'PLACEHOLDER: escogida fermentation — same leaves, month 22.';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mariposa • About — Origins image-treatment mocks">

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="intro__eyebrow">Internal &mdash; comparison surface</p>
      <h1 class="intro__title">About page &mdash; comparison mocks (revised)</h1>
      <p class="intro__lede">
        Two sections only &mdash; Origins + Story. Five image-treatment
        variants for Origins (Pax&rsquo;s
        <em>about-origins-image-research.md</em>, Part 3, Options 1&ndash;5);
        one placeholder treatment for Story so the page foot reads.
        Origins prose split across Pax&rsquo;s four beats &mdash;
        Argopuro, the seed, Jember, Time. The live
        <code>/about</code> page is unchanged.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      OPTION 1 — Alternating editorial split (left-right rhythm)
      ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}

  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option 1 &mdash; Alternating editorial split</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Two-column split per beat, image-left / image-right
        alternating beat to beat. All four beats internally identical;
        the alternation is the only variation. Landscape 4:3 across
        all images, ~1:1 image-to-prose vertical ratio. The
        Roman &amp; Williams / Aman About register applied to a
        short chronology. Lowest cognitive load of the five.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="opt opt-1" aria-label="Option 1 — Alternating editorial split">

    <section class="o-head" aria-label="Origins — opening">
      <div class="o-head__inner container">
        <p class="o-head__eyebrow">Origins</p>
        <p class="o-head__line">Where Indonesia learned to roll cigars.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o1-beat o1-beat--img-left" aria-label="Argopuro — the land">
      <div class="o1-beat__inner container">
        <figure class="placeholder placeholder--4x3" aria-label="Argopuro placeholder">
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capLand}</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="o1-beat__copy">
          <p class="o1-beat__eyebrow">{beatLandEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o1-beat__para">{beatLandBody}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o1-beat o1-beat--img-right" aria-label="The seed — twenty years">
      <div class="o1-beat__inner container">
        <div class="o1-beat__copy">
          <p class="o1-beat__eyebrow">{beatSeedEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o1-beat__para">{beatSeedBody}</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="placeholder placeholder--4x3" aria-label="The seed placeholder">
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capSeed}</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o1-beat o1-beat--img-left" aria-label="Jember — the workshop">
      <div class="o1-beat__inner container">
        <figure class="placeholder placeholder--4x3" aria-label="Jember workshop placeholder">
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capHand}</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="o1-beat__copy">
          <p class="o1-beat__eyebrow">{beatHandEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o1-beat__para">{beatHandBody}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o1-beat o1-beat--img-right" aria-label="Time — three years">
      <div class="o1-beat__inner container">
        <div class="o1-beat__copy">
          <p class="o1-beat__eyebrow">{beatTimeEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o1-beat__para">{beatTimeBody}</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="placeholder placeholder--4x3" aria-label="Ageing room placeholder">
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capTime}</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>

  {/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      OPTION 2 — Full-bleed cinematic per beat
      ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}

  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option 2 &mdash; Full-bleed cinematic per beat</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Each beat is a full-bleed landscape photograph at ~70vh, with
        eyebrow + prose anchored bottom-left over a soft gradient.
        Four cinematic scenes in sequence. Macallan / Hennessy
        register. ~95:5 image-to-prose. Highest photography burden
        of the five &mdash; needs Nick Knight-grade shots in every
        beat or the placeholders dominate the page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="opt opt-2" aria-label="Option 2 — Full-bleed cinematic">

    <section class="o-head o-head--inverse" aria-label="Origins — opening">
      <div class="o-head__inner container">
        <p class="o-head__eyebrow">Origins</p>
        <p class="o-head__line">Where Indonesia learned to roll cigars.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o2-beat" aria-label="Argopuro — the land">
      <figure class="o2-beat__frame" aria-label="Argopuro full-bleed">
        <Image src={o2Land} alt="Atmospheric placeholder standing in for Argopuro range — final shot to be commissioned." class="o2-beat__img" widths={[1200, 1800, 2400, 3200]} sizes="100vw" />
        <div class="o2-beat__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="o2-beat__placeholder-note">{o2PlaceholderNote}</p>
        <div class="o2-beat__caption">
          <p class="o2-beat__eyebrow">{beatLandEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o2-beat__para">{beatLandBody}</p>
        </div>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="o2-beat" aria-label="The seed — twenty years">
      <figure class="o2-beat__frame" aria-label="The seed full-bleed">
        <Image src={o2Seed} alt="Atmospheric placeholder standing in for the seed nursery — final shot to be commissioned." class="o2-beat__img" widths={[1200, 1800, 2400, 3200]} sizes="100vw" />
        <div class="o2-beat__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="o2-beat__placeholder-note">{o2PlaceholderNote}</p>
        <div class="o2-beat__caption">
          <p class="o2-beat__eyebrow">{beatSeedEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o2-beat__para">{beatSeedBody}</p>
        </div>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="o2-beat" aria-label="Jember — the workshop">
      <figure class="o2-beat__frame" aria-label="Jember workshop full-bleed">
        <Image src={o2Hand} alt="Atmospheric placeholder standing in for the Jember rolling room — final shot to be commissioned." class="o2-beat__img" widths={[1200, 1800, 2400, 3200]} sizes="100vw" />
        <div class="o2-beat__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="o2-beat__placeholder-note">{o2PlaceholderNote}</p>
        <div class="o2-beat__caption">
          <p class="o2-beat__eyebrow">{beatHandEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o2-beat__para">{beatHandBody}</p>
        </div>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="o2-beat" aria-label="Time — three years">
      <figure class="o2-beat__frame" aria-label="Ageing room full-bleed">
        <Image src={o2Time} alt="Atmospheric placeholder standing in for the ageing room — final shot to be commissioned." class="o2-beat__img" widths={[1200, 1800, 2400, 3200]} sizes="100vw" />
        <div class="o2-beat__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="o2-beat__placeholder-note">{o2PlaceholderNote}</p>
        <div class="o2-beat__caption">
          <p class="o2-beat__eyebrow">{beatTimeEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o2-beat__para">{beatTimeBody}</p>
        </div>
      </figure>
    </section>

  </article>

  {/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      OPTION 3 — Sticky scroll with reading rail
      ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}

  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option 3 &mdash; Sticky scroll with reading rail</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Sticky image panel left (~55vw), prose rail right (~45vw),
        beats cross-fade as the reader scrolls. Single continuous
        scene with four image-states. Aman Tokyo / scrollytelling
        register. Portrait 3:4 across all four. Most modern visually,
        highest implementation cost &mdash; mobile needs a second
        layout (falls back to Option 1). Mock below shows the static
        composition; cross-fade not wired here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="opt opt-3" aria-label="Option 3 — Sticky scroll">

    <section class="o-head" aria-label="Origins — opening">
      <div class="o-head__inner container">
        <p class="o-head__eyebrow">Origins</p>
        <p class="o-head__line">Where Indonesia learned to roll cigars.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o3-sequence" aria-label="Origins sticky sequence">
      <div class="o3-sequence__inner container">
        <div class="o3-sequence__sticky">
          <figure class="placeholder placeholder--3x4" aria-label="Sticky image panel placeholder">
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">
              PLACEHOLDER (sticky panel): four portrait images cross-fade as the reader scrolls &mdash; Argopuro, Pak Abdul Kahar Muzakir, Jember rolling room, ageing room. Static mock shows beat 1.
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="o3-sequence__rail">
          <div class="o3-sequence__beat">
            <p class="o3-sequence__eyebrow">{beatLandEyebrow}</p>
            <p class="o3-sequence__para">{beatLandBody}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="o3-sequence__beat">
            <p class="o3-sequence__eyebrow">{beatSeedEyebrow}</p>
            <p class="o3-sequence__para">{beatSeedBody}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="o3-sequence__beat">
            <p class="o3-sequence__eyebrow">{beatHandEyebrow}</p>
            <p class="o3-sequence__para">{beatHandBody}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="o3-sequence__beat">
            <p class="o3-sequence__eyebrow">{beatTimeEyebrow}</p>
            <p class="o3-sequence__para">{beatTimeBody}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>

  {/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      OPTION 4 — Asymmetric editorial, varied per beat  [REC]
      Per Pax's Part 3 spec:
        Beat 1 — full-bleed landscape ~70vh
        Beat 2 — small square inset image-right, prose-led
        Beat 3 — asymmetric editorial spread, image breaks column
        Beat 4 — diptych, two portrait images paired
      Single photographer credit on beat 3.
      ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}

  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">
        Option 4 &mdash; Asymmetric editorial, varied per beat
        <span class="label__pick">Pax&rsquo;s recommendation</span>
      </p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Each beat gets a different treatment, calibrated to the
        content. Beat 1 (Argopuro) full-bleed landscape ~70vh.
        Beat 2 (the seed) small square inset, image-right, prose-led
        ~60/40. Beat 3 (Jember) asymmetric editorial spread, image
        breaks the column ~10% past the boundary; single photographer
        credit on this beat. Beat 4 (Time) diptych &mdash; two
        portrait images flush, prose centred below. Aman About /
        Singita register; carries all five of Pax&rsquo;s editorial
        moves at maximum density.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="opt opt-4" aria-label="Option 4 — Asymmetric editorial">

    <section class="o-head" aria-label="Origins — opening">
      <div class="o-head__inner container">
        <p class="o-head__eyebrow">Origins</p>
        <p class="o-head__line">Where Indonesia learned to roll cigars.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Beat 1 — full-bleed landscape, ~70vh, type bottom-left. */}
    <section class="o4-land" aria-label="Argopuro — the land (full-bleed)">
      <figure class="o4-land__frame placeholder placeholder--bleed" aria-label="Argopuro full-bleed placeholder">
        <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <figcaption class="placeholder__caption o4-land__placeholder-caption">{capLand}</figcaption>
        <div class="o4-land__caption">
          <span class="o4-land__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <p class="o4-land__eyebrow">{beatLandEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o4-land__para">{beatLandBody}</p>
        </div>
        <p class="o4-land__credit">Argopuro range, East Java</p>
      </figure>
    </section>

    {/* Beat 2 — prose-led, small square inset image-right. */}
    <section class="o4-seed" aria-label="The seed — twenty years (prose-led, small inset)">
      <div class="o4-seed__inner container">
        <div class="o4-seed__copy">
          <p class="o4-seed__eyebrow">{beatSeedEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o4-seed__para">{beatSeedBody}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="o4-seed__media">
          <figure class="placeholder placeholder--1x1" aria-label="Pak Abdul Kahar Muzakir placeholder">
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capSeed}</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <p class="o4-seed__credit">Pak Abdul Kahar Muzakir, Jember, East Java</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Beat 3 — asymmetric editorial spread, image breaks the
        column on the right. Single photographer credit. */}
    <section class="o4-hand" aria-label="Jember — the workshop (asymmetric, image breaks column)">
      <div class="o4-hand__inner container">
        <div class="o4-hand__copy">
          <p class="o4-hand__eyebrow">{beatHandEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o4-hand__para">{beatHandBody}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="o4-hand__media">
          <figure class="placeholder placeholder--3x2" aria-label="Jember workshop placeholder">
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capHand}</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <p class="o4-hand__credit">Photograph: [Name] &mdash; Jember rolling room, 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Beat 4 — diptych, two portrait images flush, prose below. */}
    <section class="o4-time" aria-label="Time — three years (diptych)">
      <div class="o4-time__inner container">
        <div class="o4-time__diptych">
          <figure class="placeholder placeholder--4x5" aria-label="Escogida month 4 placeholder">
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capTimeA}</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="placeholder placeholder--4x5" aria-label="Escogida month 22 placeholder">
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capTimeB}</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <p class="o4-time__caption">Escogida, month 4 / month 22</p>
        <div class="o4-time__copy">
          <p class="o4-time__eyebrow">{beatTimeEyebrow}</p>
          <p class="o4-time__para">{beatTimeBody}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>

  {/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      OPTION 5 — Type-led with image as supporting touch
      ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}

  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option 5 &mdash; Type-led with image as supporting touch</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Prose dominates, one small image per beat floated inline
        (~25% column width, alternating right/left for subtle
        rhythm). All four images square, ~15:85 image-to-prose.
        Aesop / Le Labo register. Lowest photography burden of the
        five &mdash; four tight crops, manageable from a half-day
        shoot. The option that ships fastest without commissioned
        photography.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="opt opt-5" aria-label="Option 5 — Type-led">

    <section class="o-head" aria-label="Origins — opening">
      <div class="o-head__inner container">
        <p class="o-head__eyebrow">Origins</p>
        <p class="o-head__line">Where Indonesia learned to roll cigars.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="o5-beat" aria-label="Argopuro — the land">
      <div class="o5-beat__inner">
        <p class="o5-beat__eyebrow">{beatLandEyebrow}</p>
        <figure class="placeholder placeholder--1x1 o5-beat__float o5-beat__float--right" aria-label="Argopuro inline placeholder">
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <figcaption class="placeholder__caption">{capLand}</figcaption>
